                            <comment id="15028947" author="githubbot" created="Thu, 26 Nov 2015 14:59:26 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Github user StephanEwen commented on a diff in the pull request:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/1410#discussion_r45985979&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/1410#discussion_r45985979&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &amp;#8212; Diff: flink-streaming-connectors/flink-connector-kafka/src/main/java/org/apache/flink/streaming/connectors/kafka/FlinkKafkaConsumer.java &amp;#8212;&lt;br/&gt;
    @@ -415,13 +415,17 @@ public void run(SourceContext&amp;lt;T&amp;gt; sourceContext) throws Exception {&lt;br/&gt;
     				long commitInterval = Long.valueOf(props.getProperty(&quot;auto.commit.interval.ms&quot;, &quot;60000&quot;));&lt;br/&gt;
     				offsetCommitter = new PeriodicOffsetCommitter(commitInterval, this);&lt;br/&gt;
     				offsetCommitter.start();&lt;br/&gt;
    +				offsetCommitter.setDaemon(true);&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;#8212; End diff &amp;#8211;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    I think that has to be before `start()` (otherwise it fails)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
